appName: Velocity Jet Ski: Boat Racing Games
displayName: Velocity Jet Ski: Boat Racing Games
display_name: Velocity Jet Ski: Boat Racing Games
display_long_description:
Velocity Jet Ski: Boat Racing Games brings the thrill of water racing to VR. Jump onto powerful jet skis and take on challenging courses filled with sharp turns, big waves, and fast straights. Every race pushes your reflexes as you fight for control and speed on the open water.

The game delivers realistic handling, immersive VR views, and stunning water effects that make every splash feel alive. Whether you are chasing the perfect lap time or competing for first place, the excitement of jet ski racing is always in motion.

From calm beaches to intense water arenas, each course is designed to keep you on edge. Sharpen your skills, push your limits, and prove yourself as the fastest rider on the waves. Velocity Jet Ski is more than a game, it is a complete VR racing experience that puts you at the heart of the action.

**Feature:**
- Realistic jet ski physics and water handling
- Immersive VR cockpit and rider views
- Dynamic water effects with waves and splashes
- Multiple race modes including time trials and competitions
- Diverse courses from beaches to fast water tracks
- High-speed action designed for VR racing fans
